syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tatal~aEa","text_ar":"تَتَلَّعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he advanced his neck, and raised his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his eyes, looking"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for a thing, or towards a thing]. (K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTl~E A_ilaY wuruwdihi","text_ar":"تطلّع اـِلَى وُرُودِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his eyes, looking for its,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his arrival."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTal~aEotu A_ilaY","text_ar":"تَطَلَّعْتُ اـِلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuruwdi kitaAbika","text_ar":"وُرُودِ كِتَابِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I raised my eyes, looking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I looked continually,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the arrival of thy letter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, PS:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotaZarotu","text_ar":"اِنْتَظَرْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[agreeably with what here follows, and with an explanation of the inf. n. in the KL]. (PS.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTl~E A_ilaY liqaAy^ihi","text_ar":"تطلّع اـِلَى لِقَايِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked for the meeting him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) And [hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAfaY A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"عَافَى ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulFA lamo yataTal~aEo fiY famika","text_ar":"رَجُلًا لَمْ يَتَطَلَّعْ فِى فَمِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God preserve"},{"kind":"text","text":"from disease, or harm,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has not sought to find some slip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault, in thy speech:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) mentioned by AZ, (O, TA,) and by Z. (TA.) [Hence likewise,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aTal~uEu","text_ar":"التَّطَلُّعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_i$oraAfu","text_ar":"الاـِشْرَافُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The being eager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently eager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with what here follows]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aTal~uEu A_ilaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"التَّطَلُّعُ اـِلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The inclining"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the soul"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the love of the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the desiring it so that the man perishes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTal~uEu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"تَطَلُّعُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The desiring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yearning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longing, of the soul."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See an ex. in a verse cited in the first paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sbr","text_ar":"صبر"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTl~Ehu","text_ar":"تطلّعهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked at him with a look of love"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of hatred."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He overcame him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtook him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a man. (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also 6. ―         -b4-  And see 8."}],"source_refs":["O","K","S","TA","PS"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}